room_title: Escape room "The Crazy Cat Lady" by Elusive Escape Rooms in Wisconsin Dells
review: Had a blast. We completed Crazy Cat Lady. We had never done anything like this before. Our gamemaster was nice and helpful. Would definitely recommend. I would not want more than 4 people in our room.

room_title: Escape room "The Crazy Cat Lady" by Elusive Escape Rooms in Wisconsin Dells
review: My son, my nephew, and I experienced the crazy cat lady room. It is by far our favorite attraction in the Dells. It was so much fun and I recommend trying it out. It promotes teamwork and really using your brain to solve riddles and puzzles.

room_title: Escape room "The Crazy Cat Lady" by Elusive Escape Rooms in Wisconsin Dells
review: It was our first escape room and we'll be back! Alex is an awesome game master! My husband and I tried (and didn't quite make it) to concur the crazy cat lady room. We'll be back Alex!
